        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2403573982" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13293558190314406092">As difficult as I find it to read and appreciate books of poetry, I would have thought that a work in translation would be even more alienating. This selection of Nobel Prize winner Szymborska&apos;s work from 1957-93 is rendered beautifully into English. The poems wrestle with life and love and death and they do so with wit and grace. A charming collection.</span>
  <span id="freeText13293558190314406092" style="display:none">As difficult as I find it to read and appreciate books of poetry, I would have thought that a work in translation would be even more alienating. This selection of Nobel Prize winner Szymborska's work from 1957-93 is rendered beautifully into English. The poems wrestle with life and love and death and they do so with wit and grace. A charming collection.</span>
