        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1202035877" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13808690993405956303">Part of my most recent poetry binge, I finally got around to reading a Nobel Prize winner who had been on my radar for a while, but I could never find her work in poetry sections of bookstores when I was looking. <br/><br/>It&apos;s amazing. I can&apos;t tell if the poetry is so good because of or in spite of the translation, but one way or another the poems broadly range in topic but all have an incredible and brilliant spirit. <br/><br/>I&apos;ll have to find more of her poetry soon. </span>
  <span id="freeText13808690993405956303" style="display:none">Part of my most recent poetry binge, I finally got around to reading a Nobel Prize winner who had been on my radar for a while, but I could never find her work in poetry sections of bookstores when I was looking. <br /><br />It's amazing. I can't tell if the poetry is so good because of or in spite of the translation, but one way or another the poems broadly range in topic but all have an incredible and brilliant spirit. <br /><br />I'll have to find more of her poetry soon. </span>
